{"tid":2309154,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【世紀大賤男】明知人地有老婆，係都要痴埋去","createTime":"2020-12-02T10:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T11:36:11.000Z","uid":137277,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9abf65c2215ef8960c822ccec49a981ec9f114","tid":2309154,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"明知個女仔有未婚夫 <br />\n仲要主動黐埋去 想搶人老婆<br />\n俾人拒絕就要生要死<br />\n真係令人作嘔<br />\n<br />\n（好心你啦，你葫蘆身型又樣衰髮型老套都夠膽死搞人老婆）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWRhdTh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWRhdTh.jpg&h=ad6a583c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你呢個人仲幫人出櫃、爆人秘密、寫假新聞！<br />\n呢啲人真係人渣，社會嘅敗類，係垃圾人！"},{"pid":"5cf31b2080decebf13e515439d1d20e93712af01","tid":2309154,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bf3252a6b12a1d42792ba5707df40ba3eb72d996","tid":2309154,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"88be0db58a58263f19b0601eebb5d935c3d1367a","tid":2309154,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1af830be6f8b043965ebb4836444e2065a8cd080","tid":2309154,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8e84389830d38655fac98617c18158a77564b9ed","tid":2309154,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"480c5b28b3e4185097784c4d9061c78911405164","tid":2309154,"uid":371558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72cf01af526d346d843e83a19f467414429264a3","tid":2309154,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"92295dfe8bcf0be4d8ddf0387eba90def476a38e","tid":2309154,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dis